# 230 C.O.R.E. Output Format (MVP)

Role
Ensure human-facing outputs are fast to scan and decision-first.

Applies To
- /plan-review
- /spec-audit (if used)
- /spec-driven (human checkpoints)
- /postmortem (summary section only, if used)

Mandatory Format
